alerts.description:
There is a risk of light snowfall (Level 1 of 4).
Height range: > 800 m; Precipitation amounts: 1-5 cm; amount already fallen: < 25 cm

There is a risk of frost (Level 1 of 2).
Minimum temperature: 0 - -4 °C; local minimum: particularly as the sky clears over snow > -8 °C
There is a risk of icy surfaces (Level 1 of 4).
